{"tid":2102082,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民主派就《禁蒙面法》申終審法院上訴許可獲批","createTime":"2020-07-10T08:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T12:29:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":140,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"b618a35e47169fbf0545fa7bd206efbd967813b3","tid":2102082,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/CACV000541B_2019.docx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2019%2FCACV000541B_2019.docx&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=86008df7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/CACV000541B_2019.docx</a><br />\n<br />\n《禁蒙面法》司法覆核案上訴庭在四月裁定港府部份上訴得直，即《禁蒙面法》在非法集結及未經批准集結的情況下仍然生效，民主派向高等法院申請終審法院上訴許可，上訴庭指案件涉及重大的公眾利益，故批出終審法院上訴許可。"},{"pid":"2c79cd417a391df0ce89cd85d8086e0db7b078f7","tid":2102082,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740f46e92ded4fae2a9810966e4c0e17abdf46be","tid":2102082,"uid":202464,"like":21,"dislike":7,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"703e104fdb1749936bd26a4d5e6c6f248391b424","tid":2102082,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c79cd417a391df0ce89cd85d8086e0db7b078f7","tid":2102082,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hk